  Anysphere’s revenue and usage has also been growing fast, one person said.
  
  In July, Business Insider [reported](https://www.businessinsider.com/ai-startup-anysphere-raises-a-new-funding-round-from-a16z-2024-7) that Anysphere was in the process of raising a new round and aiming for a $400 million valuation.
  
