  [Tech](https://www.businessinsider.com/tech)
  
  # Exclusive: AI coding startup Anysphere is raising a new funding round with at least a $400 million valuation from A16z
  
  By[Sri Muppidi](https://www.businessinsider.com/author/sri-muppidi)
  
  ![Developer, programmer, software developer coding](https://i.insider.com/64ff6a3f4b33390019f0b33d?width=700)
  
  Anysphere's Cursor is an AI code editor for engineers.valentinrussanov/Getty Images
  
  Jul 15, 2024, 9:21 PM ET
  
  SaveSaved[Read in app](https://insider-app.onelink.me/4cpG/?af_js_web=true&af_ss_ver=2_3_0&af_dp=insider%3A%2F%2Fbi%2Fpost%2Fai-startup-anysphere-raises-a-new-funding-round-from-a16z-2024-7&af_force_deeplink=true&is_retargeting=true&deep_link_value=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-anysphere-raises-a-new-funding-round-from-a16z-2024-7&pid=businessinsider&c=post_page_share_bar_v2_smart_4.13.23 "Download the app")
  
